For a ecommerce application if there is only 1 phone and at the same time
and there are multiple customer for same phone and ordered at same time, how you will make sure
this transaction is successful for only 1 customer and other customers will get a message that phone is out of stock.
Ans: lock the resource (phone) when a customer is trying to purchase it. This can be achieved using synchronization or by using a database transaction with appropriate isolation levels. When a customer initiates the purchase, acquire a lock on the phone resource. If another customer tries to purchase the same phone while it is locked, they will receive a message that the phone is out of stock. Once the first customer's transaction is completed and the lock is released, other customers can attempt to purchase the phone again.
